            . I saw the prisoner at the bar, bring a copper out of No. 1, <placeName id="t18150913-27-crimeloc142">Red Lion-market, Whitecross-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150913-27-crimeloc142" type="placeName" value="Red Lion-market, Whitecross-street"></interp>
